Detailed Description

cvmx_usbdrd::_uahc_gdbgltssm

In multiport host configuration, the port number is defined by USBDRD()_UAHC_GDBGFIFOSPACE[SELECT]<3:0>. Value of this register may change immediately after reset. See description in USBDRD()_UAHC_GDBGFIFOSPACE.

This register can be reset by IOI reset or with USBDRD()_UCTL_CTL[UAHC_RST].
